Mistake #1: 'Make' vs. 'Do' 

9
00:00:50,160 --> 00:00:56,580
"Make" and "do" are both action words in English. 
They can be tricky for people learning English  

10
00:00:56,580 --> 00:01:04,440
because sometimes they are used in similar ways.
"Do" is often used when talking about work, jobs,  

11
00:01:04,440 --> 00:01:13,740
