do the laundry. She does a lot of work every day. 

12
00:01:13,740 --> 00:01:17,580
Actions that are regular 
or routine often use "do." 

13
00:01:17,580 --> 00:01:25,320
For example. I do the dishes every 
evening. He does the shopping on Saturdays. 

14
00:01:25,320 --> 00:01:29,700
"Make" is used when we 
create or produce something. 

15
00:01:29,700 --> 00:01:37,020
For example: She made a cake for my birthday. 
They are making a documentary about wildlife. 

16
00:01:37,020 --> 00:01:43,440
